\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Interpretation of definition 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Consider-any-mechanism"

\end_inset

 for mechanisms contracting on reductions in deforestation and on universal
 cash transfers: Throughout this article we will interpret
