\end_inset

 
\emph on
to be the reduction in deforestation and
\emph default
 
\begin_inset Formula $x^{B}$
\end_inset

 
\emph on
to be the value of the universal cash transfers.
 The type-compementarity property means in this context the following: Consider
 two governments with payoffs that are identical in terms of their costs
 of reducing deforestation.
 Then at the optimal mechanism the one that is more enthusiastic about universal
