\series bold
Lemma 0.0:
\series default
 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{M}_{A,B}^{\text{first\ b}\text{est}}$
\end_inset

 denote the optimal joint mechanism (contracting jointly on deforestation
 reduction and universal cash transfers) when the principal knows each agent's
 type and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{M}_{A}^{\text{first\ best}},\ \mathcal{M}_{B}^{\text{first\ best}}$
\end_inset

 the optimal separate mechanisms (contracting only on the reduction in deforesta
tion and only on the universal cash transfer, respectively) when the principal
